                                    p
                                        strong...wxPython 4.2.2
                                        .is now available at
                                        a href=https://pypi.org/project/wxPython/4.2.2...PyPI
                                        ., with some additional files at
                                        a href=https://extras.wxpython.org/wxPython4/extras/...Extras
                                    p...Changes in this release:
                                    ul
                                        li
                                            p...This release was built using the wxWidgets' v3.2.6 release tag. This is the first release built using GitHub infrastructure instead of the buildbots. Please report any problems with the wheels.
                                        li
                                            p...Fix some Python 3.12 compatibility issues (segfault on exit) by upgrading sip & waf
                                        li
                                            p...Fix more float/int conversion issues in wx.lib classes (#2415, #2417, #2429, #2470, #2528, #2542)
                                        li
                                            p...Add initialValue argument to wx.lib.DirBrowseButton (#2430)
                                        li
                                            p...Fix wxImage.Clear() (#2433)
                                        li
                                            p...Fix blurry text in AuiNotebook tab (#2360)
                                        li
                                            p...Add support for frozen rows and columns to GridWithLabelRenderersMixin (#2436)
                                        li
                                            p...demo: ShortcutEditor: Fix broken call GetMenuBar() (#2412)
                                        li
                                            p...Add proper support for DataViewCheckIconTextRenderer (#2425)
                                        li
                                            p...Remove legacy macOS logic, use wx.SystemSettings to select colors (#2018)
                                        li
                                            p...Build: Use new tarfile.extractall() filter for safer tarfile extraction (#2443)
                                        li
                                            p...Fix typo in wx.lib.agw.persist_handlers (#2469)
                                        li
                                            p...Fix 'str' to 'wxString' converstation, when emoji is inside string (#2446)
                                        li
                                            p...Use unwrap before isbuiltin check (#2487)
                                        li
                                            p...Preserve pane icons when loading a perspective in agw.aui (#2494)
                                        li
                                            p...wx.agw.aui: don't uninitialize the AuiManager if the window close event is vetoed (#2460)
                                        li
                                            p...Pure python AUI: Make behavior in all platforms more equal (#2501)
                                        li
                                            p...wx.agw.aui. Do layout as the last step after all pane infos have recomputed their best sizes (#2500)
                                        li
                                            p...Fix additional SyntaxWarnings with Python 3.12 (#2502)
                                        li
                                            p...Fix wx.lib.agw.ribbon.RibbonButtonBar DeleteButton function (#2511)
                                        li
                                            p...UltimateListCtrl: Add support for ULC_AUTO_CHECK_PARENT (#2518)
                                        li
                                            p...Remove dependency on distutils (#2519)
                                        li
                                            p...Improve wx.lib.agw.FlatMenu memory usage (#2373)
                                        li
                                            p...Support NumPy 2.0 (#2580, 2591)
                                        li
                                            p...Fix EditLabel on CustomTreeCtrl doesn't automatically select the entire text (#2549)
                                        li
                                            p...Fix Widgets placed in the UltimateListControl are drawn in the wrong location (#2410)
                                        li
                                            p...Fix wx.lib.agw.aui sometimes shows "ghost" docking guide (#2364)
                                        li
                                            p...Fix Thumbnailctrl SetSelection raises exception if it tries to scroll (#2345)
